III. REQUIREMENTS IN IRAQ BY FINANCE AND ACTIVITY PLAN CATEGORY
A. T&E

CJTF-OIR conducts A2E efforts with vetted partner forces to independently sustain the enduring defeat of ISIS and prevent its
remnants from rebuilding a capability to threaten the Homeland. CTEF T&E procurements ensure the continued development of
partnered force capabilities to defeat ISIS remnants without U.S. or coalition assistance, which follows DoW’s two lines of effort: the
denial of ISIS safe havens and the building of partner force capabilities to ensure the enduring defeat of ISIS remnants.

