INSERT INTO public.om_sag_narratives (sag_id, fiscal_year, mission_description, justification, raw_text, source_pdf, source_page_description, source_page_amount, content_hash, ingested_at) VALUES ($$om_comp_0605$$, 2026, $$R&D Engineering Development — Activity Code 0605: System Development & Demonstration.

This Combat and Operational Medicine Program (COMP) RDT&E sub-activity funds the system development & demonstration portfolio executed by the Defense Health Agency (DHA). It is one of seven RDT&E activity-code categories under COMP appropriation 0130D, Budget Activity 02.

This sub-activity aggregates the following Program Elements in the FY 2027 President's Budget R-1 (Defense Health Agency):
  - PE 0605013 — Information Technology Development
  - PE 0605045 — Joint Operational Medicine Information System
  - PE 0605145 — Medical Products and Support Systems Development
  - PE 0605039 — DoW Medical Information Exchange and
  - PE 0605502 — Small Business Innovative Research

Per-PE technical narratives, project justification, and quantitative justification appear in the MHS J-Book Volume 1 (Exhibit R-2 / R-2A, starting at page 179) and Volume 2 (SMR projects). Funding totals are summarized in Exhibit R-1 "RDT&E Programs" on page 177.$$, NULL, NULL, $$Budget J-Books/FY27/MHS/MHS_PB27_J-Book-Vol1-COMP_PSCP.pdf$$, 177, 177, $$172e2f46f57d89c4aff93313328e3acd76e7679c76584e8f54a07e3ee7125808$$, $$2026-05-09T21:43:13.101023+00:00$$) ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
