E. SUSTAINMENT

Sustaining CTEF procured vehicles, facilities, and equipment is critical to ensuring partner forces retain the capability to conduct
D-ISIS operations. Sustainment funding will support partner force logistical operations, including supply, services, base
operations, and maintenance. These funds would also ensure repair parts are available for VSGI at full capability. Facility
sustainment and operating costs include basic provisions required for ongoing operations for the enduring defeat of ISIS.
