Cyberspace activities fund Offensive Cyber Operations (OCO) to defend the nation against strategic cyber-attacks, Defensive Cyber Operations (DCO) to operate and
defend Department of Defense information networks (DoDIN), and US critical infrastructure. Directly supports USCYBERCOM Cyber Mission Forces, Combatant
